      <title>委内瑞拉观察人士称马杜罗将寻求逃避最新制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/venezuela-watchers-say-maduro-will-seek-to-evade-latest-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉活动人士和政策分析人士呼吁实施更严厉的制裁，并调查总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗政府如何使用加密货币来规避国际限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/venezuela-watchers-say-maduro-will-seek-to-evade-latest-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
